{"tid":2455693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門建生邨舉行法團周年大會 前民建聯區議員陳文華斥記者「曱甴」「黑暴」","createTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:36:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f6246a344a87a95170a7d2016252840d799ddaf","tid":2455693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"屯門建生邨今早舉行法團周年大會，民建聯前當區區議員陳文華陰魂不散，先在會場內打點一切，包括落order街坊投票支持豁免半年管理費，又在場內「唱衰」現任民主派區議員羅佩麗，「俾啲人嘥哂建生啲錢。」<br />\n<br />\n獨媒記者曾向陳文華查詢，問到以甚麼身份進入會場，及是否干預法團事務。他拒絕回應，反斥記者是曱甴，又煽動其他街坊指罵記者和建生邨居民關注組成員，「呢啲就係黑暴。」<br />\n<br />\n在法團周年會議完畢後，記者離遠拍攝陳文華時，他和身旁的女義工激動拿出手機反拍記者，陳文華又一度走到記者旁並稱：「一齊影啦！」其後更一直追隨記者錄影，其義工更指罵記者。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今次會議動用近10萬元開支。「建生邨居民關注組」成員姜先生表示，對開會登記的安排表示不滿，因原本會議於早上10時開始登記，但街坊在場外等候至10時20分才獲准入內登記，原本11時開始的會議拖延一小時後才開始。姜生不解為何場內有近20名工作人員，但他們手腳慢，「人龍郁得好得慢，搞到一鑊泡，要啲街坊淋住雨等」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081573\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081573&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=3556cdc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1081573&h=611cd272\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1081573</a>"},{"pid":"761f9801461b9be967e6361a0faf1e361dc5f988","tid":2455693,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712c49cb146d4ed679d53eacf2e74432c517a99a","tid":2455693,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a04001e6dbd01aa39a23b47a48457d9008c0573","tid":2455693,"uid":65888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"忠誠的廢物都無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9554d9f97e7051d5327f39c7ba80ab7b80dfdb35","tid":2455693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a04001e6dbd01aa39a23b47a48457d9008c0573","tid":2455693,"uid":65888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"忠誠的廢物都無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a90d72c0a13678bf044d52a7accc0a366311b77","tid":2455693,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"712c49cb146d4ed679d53eacf2e74432c517a99a","tid":2455693,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T10:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"h